{"tid":1085291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：看不到逃犯條例較基本法23條更惡","createTime":"2019-03-31T05:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T09:18:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a05f0254c7fff824865e699747791830faa18f65","tid":1085291,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161023/large/23la3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161023%2Flarge%2F23la3p4.jpg&h=e40f86a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠指，修訂逃犯條例只是處理移交逃犯問題，過程須符合國際標準，質疑有人指這次修例比基本法23條更嚴重的批評。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠又指，如逃犯條例修訂獲通過，將為處理台灣殺人案移除很大的障礙。又指樂見可就貪污罪移交逃犯，認為對香港作為國際金融中心有很大幫助。"},{"pid":"2f9735a10e15604346deb6340d1c029574a54fa0","tid":1085291,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=342815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342815&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=f44ec848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342815&h=69fe43d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=342815</a>"},{"pid":"ad64c4c9a57adb54596517d13b5858f78681c7ab","tid":1085291,"uid":103230,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:04:09.000Z","msg":"鬼拍後尾枕<br />\n認23條惡喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6592b7af7ae7e3e376652421c44e513d0a8bbaeb","tid":1085291,"uid":54959,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"直接承認23 條好惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha